external_knowledge:
- "dawn of the active user era" refers to the earliest date when an active user account was created;
- "digital garden" is a metaphor for the database or system where user accounts are stored;
- Active user accounts are those where `is_active` is set to 1.

sql:
SELECT MIN(created_on) AS dawn_of_the_active_user_era
FROM users
WHERE is_active = 1;

